name: Delta Air Lines Airbus A350-900 Taxi and Takeoff from Los Angeles
description:
Despite being in commercial service for 3 years now, this is actually my first time filming an Airbus A350! Delta became the first American operator of the A350 just over a year ago, with this exact aircraft, N501DN, seen here departing Los Angeles International Airport for Shanghai as "Delta 89 heavy". The A350's definitely grown on me since we first saw it, those winglets look fantastic! Glad to have finally filmed one.

Thanks for watching!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

FLIGHT INFORMATION
Airline: Delta Air Lines (DAL/DL)
Aircraft: Airbus A350-941 (A359)
Flight Number: DL89
Livery: New
Engines: 2x RR Trent XWB-84 
Registration: N501DN
Route: Los Angeles (LAX) - Shanghai (PVG)
Callsign: DELTA 89 heavy
Runway used: 25R
Date filmed: November 2018
Local time: 1400
